---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Brandon Camenisch and this blog."
  pubDate={new Date('March 24 2026')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <p>
    I’m Brandon Camenisch. This blog is a place to publish technical notes, research, system
    design ideas, and progress updates from the projects I’m actively building.
  </p>

  <p>
    The focus is practical work: offensive and defensive security experimentation, Linux desktop
    and homelab automation, self-hosting, developer tooling, and the occasional essay about how
    these systems fit together.
  </p>

  <p>
    Because the site is static and repo-backed, it’s easy to keep under version control, review
    changes carefully, and publish to GitHub Pages with minimal moving parts.
  </p>
</Layout>
